data.title: Login Page for BambooHR Users
data.meta_description: BambooHR lets you focus on people, not processes. Login to BambooHR to manage your employee data, request PTO, and see new employees
data.text:
What's my BambooHR domain?

Take a look at the address bar when you are logged in to BambooHR (or ask a colleague, since you are not logged in). The text just before .bamboohr.com is your domain.
